    "en": {
      "title": "Chaminda Calumpriya granted bail",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Additional Magistrate Mr. Keminda Perera has today ( 22) ordered.",
        "The suspect who was handed over to the Kuruduwatta Police in connection with this incident was presented to the court today (22) when the arrested police presented these facts.",
        "On the 15th, the court had ordered the release of the first suspect, social activist Dhanish Ali, on two sureties of Rs 25,000 cash and Rs 5 lakh each.",
        "The third suspect, M. On the 15th, the court ordered to ban Chandimal and others from traveling abroad.",
        "The fourth suspect, Arachchige Susil Wasantha, was arrested by the Kuruduwatta police and presented to the court on the 15th, and the court ordered that the suspect be remanded until the 29th."
      ],
